The paper is about an AI-assisted code completion system, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The system uses deep learning models trained on code contexts, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The system is designed to work at a high throughput, which involves performance optimization (cs.PL) and the use of efficient algorithms. Finally, the system is an example of AI application in software development, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category.
